ABS Housing GCI
Power Hub to power a gauge & Interface 1x Ethernet port for Series 9 Gauge & 2x Ethernet Ports for Networking (+ 1 RJ45 port) Control Multi Gauges in a Network (upto 16) 10 inch Touch screen HMI Full gauge control software Embedded calibration tools Options to add Analogue or Digital interfaces and also Profibus and DeviceNet communications
